{"tid":1237842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日開咁多記招...在下有小小建議","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:26:25.000Z","uid":249001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64b622cd467ba0d0c058e6bed702ed1b53bd8544","tid":1237842,"uid":249001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"連日黎不停開記招<br />\n聽d高官舞撚晒龍舞撚晒獅咁，<br />\n建議以後佢地開記招時使用測謊機<br />\n一個記招講咁多大話<br />\n電撚到班柒頭on99咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n測謊機藉著量度和記錄血壓、脈搏、呼吸和皮膚導電反應等由交感神經引起的生理反應，來判斷正在回答問題的受測者是否說謊。由於此類生理反應是不由自主地產生的，說謊而引起此類生理反應的變化被認為能透露出受測者是否說謊。<br />\n<br />\nwikipedia <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jteYD48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjteYD48.png&h=0d227913&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50df0d560b7e0dbb15adbe30c2085fa5173cd4a9","tid":1237842,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4fab80b521a697e686dc8c014e228fbf67e69979","tid":1237842,"uid":249001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"自pish"}]}